{"tid":2404272,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"退出大灣區？莊士中國以最多15.6億人民幣出售番禺商住項目","createTime":"2021-02-11T15:11:23.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-12T18:26:06.000Z","uid":79563,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"63612ed4517e8e755794857bf24ca50ea903803b","tid":2404272,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T15:11:23.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1575365-20210211.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1575365-20210211.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=fMmZVRBh8JxXvfCabRklGS3KoYHjImyLH66vjnFGY4M%3D&h=303ce188\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1575365-20210211.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=bfa61e17\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1575365-20210211.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n莊士中國公布，以最多約15.64億元人民幣，出售番禺商住發展項目的在建部分。作價包括項目第三期和存貨的協定價值、建築費返還，和遞延稅項金額等。集團預計，出售所得淨額約13.29億元。<br />\n<br />\n發展項目合共有三期，第三期項目佔地約9.58萬平方米，可出售樓面面積約16.3萬平方米。項目已分階段發展第三期，約8.56萬平方米的範圍正進行建築工程，並已完成住宅樓宇地庫、幼稚園及公共設施之地基工程，幼稚園上蓋工程亦已完成。第一期及第二期所有物業經已售出。<br />\n<br />\n集團指，鑑於新型肺炎疫情的不確定因素，認為出售事項是集團加快取得該項目的投資及可觀盈利回報之良機，亦可於完成時獲取重大現金流入。<br />\n<br />\n莊士中國和莊士機構已向聯交所申請下周二復牌。"},{"pid":"b52971ebbde491990874663d4ca9c36398d0fa7a","tid":2404272,"uid":306614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T15:13:17.000Z","msg":"咁樣趕住賣 有咩風？"},{"pid":"d5803867c8c0afda0246035e4b2d0e4eda7e5177","tid":2404272,"uid":274149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T16:10:24.000Z","msg":"佢之前好愛國㗎"},{"pid":"4103d3924bf27adbb8e3136e6d04aab917752de8","tid":2404272,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d5803867c8c0afda0246035e4b2d0e4eda7e5177","tid":2404272,"uid":274149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T16:10:24.000Z","msg":"佢之前好愛國㗎"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-12T18:26:06.000Z","msg":"錢同愛國<br />\n<br />\n當然係揀錢"}]}